<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2B2D42;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2B2D42;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Email Confirmation</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello,</p>

            <p>Thank you for registering with us! To complete your registration and activate your account, please verify your email address.</p>

            <div class="message-box">
                <p>This verification link will expire in {{ expiresAtMessageKey|trans(expiresAtMessageData, 'VerifyEmailBundle') }}.</p>
            </div>

            <p>Click the button below to verify your email address:</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ signedUrl }}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2B2D42; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Verify Email</a>
            </div>

            <p>If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>The echriPC Team</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date('Y') }} echriPC. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>